Mail-Postini version 0.12
=========================

Mail::Postini makes LWP (web or http) requests to a Postini
application server, allowing you to create and delete organizations,
domains, and users, among other things.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  LWP::UserAgent
  Crypt::SSLeay (or other crypto module that will let LWP connect via https)
  HTML::Form
  URI::Escape
  Digest::SHA1

